{"tid":1108760,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同前女友去旅行 有冇機會復合？","createTime":"2019-04-16T06:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T07:04:42.000Z","uid":158832,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c7ed5c331e2c3c67783cc3e95512d7f639b60d2f","tid":1108760,"uid":158832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:14:14.000Z","msg":"我同ex已經分開左4，5年<br />\n<br />\n當年拍拖時都只係幾個月貨仔<br />\n因為要出國讀書關係，嗌左場交就冇挽留佢（因為學校功課嗌交）<br />\n<br />\n每年暑假返香港我都會返黎搵佢<br />\n到畢業我都想搵返佢復合，話仲中意佢<br />\n但奈何佢都唔肯，話冇左以前果種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地呢幾年都keep住wtsapp contact<br />\n但每次約佢，佢都推我，一年約得兩三次左右<br />\n而且每次見面只係食餐飯就走，見得兩三個鍾就掟我走<br />\n最初見返都試過錫佢拖佢，呢年佢連掂都唔比我掂<br />\n<br />\n佢話要我養倒佢先會同我一齊，我岩岩畢業點敢話養倒佢，所以我話30歲先得，叫佢等我，佢話好<br />\n<br />\n有次佢老母逼佢去相親，佢都話我好過個相親對象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上個禮拜佢同朋友打算下個月去台灣旅行，但比人甩底<br />\n我自動請英話不如同我去，請埋佢搭飛機，半推半就咁竟然應承同我一齊去<br />\n<br />\n不過佢話只係當我朋友咁去，費事我期望咁多<br />\n我話你當係相親咪得囉，佢話我傻<br />\n<br />\n可能大家都會覺得我傻，但終於有機會同佢朝夕相對<br />\n我希望比個好既回憶佢令佢回心轉意[b"},{"pid":"fb46c4b5f79f9d6b000db71693dc3371d7d0439f","tid":1108760,"uid":13418,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:19:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢話要我養倒佢先會同我一齊</span></span>"},{"pid":"a108ccbdb33c404cb3f82176b171168ee3395cce","tid":1108760,"uid":118647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:20:19.000Z","msg":"炮友"},{"pid":"427388d32004bdba6439290b193b2f0e8018a3c3","tid":1108760,"uid":125168,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:23:53.000Z","msg":"擺明當你back up plan多個選擇咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6695cd415703db16eb75b4d1e3660f9bcd7f58f0","tid":1108760,"uid":77643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:26:15.000Z","msg":"做住後備先囉"},{"pid":"559b6a648a7bc1dfe906e13e0f3ff5aaf045cda2","tid":1108760,"uid":158832,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"427388d32004bdba6439290b193b2f0e8018a3c3","tid":1108760,"uid":125168,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:23:53.000Z","msg":"擺明當你back up plan多個選擇咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:30:18.000Z","msg":"到最後都要選擇既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人人都想住豪宅，最後咪住返間豆潤咁細既屋"},{"pid":"669718e9cf6d6054ecd83bc2252db4f5f6e1451b","tid":1108760,"uid":158832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb46c4b5f79f9d6b000db71693dc3371d7d0439f","tid":1108760,"uid":13418,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:19:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢話要我養倒佢先會同我一齊</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:31:22.000Z","msg":"唔通同大劉一齊果d又貪佢靚仔性格好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f035e8be326a22b0232537a9c3950562a657ed89","tid":1108760,"uid":52194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:32:23.000Z","msg":"二等兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"073260141370614d8d715725fd688998d8539c94","tid":1108760,"uid":53261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:33:01.000Z","msg":"小心要養便宜仔"},{"pid":"194a8dd17dd3b07c344bcfc1e2fb20ae121c39ed","tid":1108760,"uid":20325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:33:47.000Z","msg":"下士"},{"pid":"d3de976c0640cd27b56f45cb2e2089165e43a867","tid":1108760,"uid":158832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"194a8dd17dd3b07c344bcfc1e2fb20ae121c39ed","tid":1108760,"uid":20325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:33:47.000Z","msg":"下士"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:35:15.000Z","msg":"Tamama二等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=